      "acceptanceCriteria": "Continuum elastic-plastic model with isotropic hardening appropriate for titanium alloy pedicle screw under quasi-static bending; contact modeled with Coulomb friction.",
      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V elastic-plastic constitutive model with Ramberg-Osgood hardening used. Coulomb friction (mu=0.2) at screw-block interface. Large-deformation kinematics enabled. Model form consistent with prior FDA-published FEA studies of F1717 constructs."
