    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All three QoIs satisfy E/uval < 1.96 and percentage difference < 10% acceptance bounds. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-requirement factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted on the basis that the single quasi-static loading rate tested is conservative and consistent with ASTM F1717 standard practice. Overall credibility is sufficient to support regulatory submission for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw design.",
